		"name": "SkillLink API — Web Services Demo",
		"description": "Complete Postman collection for demonstrating SkillLink Web Services.\n\n🔧 **Setup:**\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Set environment variable `base_url` to `http://localhost:5005`\n3. Run 'Login as Admin' first — it auto-saves the JWT token\n4. All protected endpoints will automatically use the saved token\n\n📌 **Test Credentials:**\n- Admin: admin@skilllink.com / Admin@123\n- Customer: ananya@example.com / Customer@123\n- Worker: rajesh@skilllink.com / Worker@123\n- Seller: mahesh@skilllink.com / Seller@123\n- Delivery: raju@skilllink.com / Delivery@123\n- Verifier: verifier@skilllink.com / Verifier@123",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:5005",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "refreshToken",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
